snippet.title: CoH2: Master Collection - Official Trailer
snippet.description:
ESRB Rating:  MATURE with Blood and Gore, Intense Violence, Strong Language

----

Join the highest rated WWII RTS franchise with this package regrouping the original COH2 and all its expansions (The Western Front Armies, Ardennes Assault and The British Forces) – as well as the Theater of War mission packs. Includes 2 single-player campaigns and 5 multiplayer armies.

www.companyofheroes.com
